	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Binas tuas accepi et intellexi studium tuum erga me, pro qua re tibi ago gratias immensas relaturus etiam data occasione.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi sessiones <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinorum</placeName> patrum, legam et bona fide per certum virum remittam.<note type="margin">dazu a.R.: "Imo accepit <persName type="auto_name">Cęlius</persName> noster, qui mihi altera die mutuo dedit."</note></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum heus tu, mitto ad te propositiones, quas d. <persName ref="p8298" cert="high">Borrhaus</persName> noster protrudit hoc periculoso tempore; sapiunt <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2301">Osiandricum</persName> dogma.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cupio itaque scire, quid de illis sentias quidve iudices.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Disputarunt nostri, sed ne verbulo attigerunt propositiones de iustitia <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2301">Osiandrica</persName>, quia non legerunt illius dogma.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid si pergat nostram turbare ecclesiam homo plenus dogmatum?</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expecto tuam hac de re sententiam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeterea mitto apologiam regis <persName type="auto_name">Gallici</persName> contra <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesaris</persName> scriptum et hoc soleo mirari, cur nullam faciat mentionem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1122">Parmensis</placeName> belli.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De novis rebus hec habemus: <persName type="auto_name">Martinus de Rossa</persName> collegit militem in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20">Inferiore Germania</placeName> nomine <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesaris</persName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aquarum inundatio magnum detrimentum dedit Prabantinis.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Norembergae 300 et quinquaginta domus combustae sunt, miserabile spectaculum.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non procul ab <placeName type="auto_name">Ambergo</placeName> ecclesia in rure multis signis clara et anathematibus ornata combusta est, et nemo ausus accedere ad reprimendum incendium; e cęlo tactum est templum, sicque idololatriam dominus delevit eo in loco.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinis</placeName> hypocritis suam manum ostenderet, quo tandem cessarent os in cęlum ponere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audio miraculum quoddam accidisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName>, quum canerent die quodam officium de spiritu sancto, volavit in templum super altare ulula, quam et cęperunt, quę evertit calicem in altario.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic solet spiritus sanctus venire ad patres istos sanctissimos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt <persName ref="p18449" cert="high">Danum</persName> habere ingentem exercitum in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l754">Holsatia</placeName>, quem in locum sit missurus militem, adhuc ignoratur.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Turbabitur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> ab omnibus partibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fertur fama conclusum fuisse a Caesareanis, ut episcopi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germani</placeName> mitterentur in <placeName ref="l875" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Hispaniam</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanos</placeName> in <placeName ref="l822" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName>, quo melior tranquillitas ecclesiae possit constitui; sed fabulam puto esse.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed hoc certum est, nemo episcoporum audebit discedere sine consensu <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesaris</persName> ex isto colloquio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt insuper <persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Philippum Melanchthonem</persName> <placeName ref="l361" cert="high">Norimbergae</placeName> fuisse, sed iterum revocatum a principe; alias periisset bonus et pius vir.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustani</placeName> concionatores mirum in modum olei unctionem et instituerunt iuxta baptismum unctionem ab episcopo consecratam; nebulones sunt, et quicquid hactenus docuerunt, iam ostendunt se ex animo nunquam bono docuisse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName> 19. februarii 1552.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An den wolgelerten herren meyster <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrych Bullingeren</persName>, lutpriester zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zurich</placeName>, mynem gunstigen herren zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
